Revision history for App-GamesWordlist

0.16    2016-02-14 (PERLANCAR)

	- No functional changes.

	- Adjust to App::lcpan::Call 0.07.


0.15    2016-01-18 (PERLANCAR)

        - No functional changes.

        - [build] Rebuild to fix POD section ordering.


0.14    2016-01-07 (PERLANCAR)

	- No functional changes.

	- No need to show examples' result (which are large).


0.13    2016-01-07 (PERLANCAR)

        - Rename module/script from App::wordlist/wordlist to
          App::GamesWordlist/games-wordlist. This is to make way for the new
          App::wordlist which will be based on WordList::*.


0.12    2016-01-04 (PERLANCAR)

	- Implement -L (list_cpan action).


0.11    2015-09-03 (PERLANCAR)

	- No functional changes.

	- [dist] Move spec prereqs from RuntimeRequires to
	  DevelopRecommends to reduce deps but still allow indicating spec
	  requirement.


0.10    2015-01-03 (PERLANCAR)

	- No functional changes.

	- Rebuild (Generate TODO.md).


0.09    2014-12-18 (PERLANCAR)

	- No functional changes.

        - [build] Rebuild with newer DZP::GenShellCompletion (0.07) (fixes).


0.08    2014-12-18 (PERLANCAR)

	- No functional changes.

        - [build] Rebuild with newer DZP::GenShellCompletion (0.06) that skips
          running shcompgen on non-POSIX systems.


0.07    2014-12-18 (PERLANCAR)

	- No functional changes.

	- [dist] Let's try again adding Complete::Util as prereq on
	  Windows.


0.06    2014-12-18 (PERLANCAR)

	- No functional changes.

	- [dzil] Make Complete::Util prereq for unix only for now,
	  Complete::Util doesn't pass test on Windows, ref:
	  http://blog.nu42.com/2014/12/when-bits-dont-stick.html.


0.05    2014-12-16 (PERLANCAR)

	- [Incompatible change] Rename --{min,max}len to --{min,max}-len to
	  be consistent with my other namings.


0.04    2014-12-11 (PERLANCAR)

	- Add options: --len, --minlen, --maxlen.

	- [ux] Don't show border for list action without detail.


0.03    2014-12-05 (PERLANCAR)

	- [ux] Don't show border when grepping, but still show border as
	  usual when listing modules.


0.02    2014-12-04 (PERLANCAR)

        - No functional changes.

        - Re-upload.


0.01    2014-12-04 (PERLANCAR)

        - First release.
